rmally pronounced ‘Water’."],"variants":[{"name":"Walther","meanings":["from <i>wald</i> ‘rule’ + <i>heri</i> ‘army’; name of the famous medieval minnesinger  Walther von der Vogelweide  (  <i>c.</i>1170– <i>c.</i>1230 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Walter Parles Sheriff was born about 1300, in Watford, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom, his father, John Parles Lord of Watford, was 32 and his mother, Eleanor, was 22. He married Alice Walter about 1328. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died on 24 July 1361, at the age of 62, and was buried in Watford, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"Abt 1309–24 July 1361":"umbes 1300–24. juuli 1361","1300–1361":"1300–1361","1315–Female":"1315–Surnud","1335–1420":"1335–1420","1270–Male":"1270–Surnud","1280–1346":"1280–1346","Abt 1309":"umbes 1300","1362":"1362","1361":"1361","1270":"1270","1280":"1280","1315":"1315","1335":"1335","1346":"1346","about 1328":"umbes 1328","1300":"1300","1420":"1420","24 July 1361":"24. juuli 1361","about 1298":"umbes 1298","Watford, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom":"Watford, Northamptonshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England"},"fi":{"Abt 1309–24 July 1361":"noin 1300–24. heinäkuuta 1361","1300–1361":"1300–1361","1315–Female":"1315–Kuollut","1335–1420":"1335–1420","1270–Male":"1270–Kuollut","1280–1346":"1280–1346","Abt 1309":"noin 1300","1362":"1362","1361":"1361","1270":"1270","1280":"1280","1315":"1315","1335":"1335","1346":"1346","about 1328":"noin 1328","1300":"1300","1420":"1420","24 July 1361":"24. heinäkuuta 1361","about 1298":"noin 1298","Watford, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom":"Watford, Northamptonshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England"},"fr":{"Abt 1309–24 July 1361":"environ 1300–24 juillet 1361","1300–1361":"1300–1361","1315–Female":"1315–Décédée","1335–1420":"1335–1420","1270–Male":"1270–Décédé","1280–1346":"1280–1346","Abt 1309"